msgstr "Seleccione su Estrategia para la misión:"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/cut_escape"
msgid "Destroy 10 german vehicles!"
msgstr "¡Destruye 10 vehículos alemanes!"

#, boost-format
msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/cut_escape_progress"
msgid "%1% out of 10 german vehicles destroyed."
msgstr "%1% de 10 vehículos alemanes destruidos."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/date"
msgid "August 7th, 1944 · Mortain, Normandy, France"
msgstr "7 de agosto de 1944 - Mortain, Normandía, Francia"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/flank"
msgid "Flank the panther through the hedgerows and take it out!"
msgstr "¡Flanquea al Panther a través de los setos y elimínalo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/name"
msgid "Mortain Counterattack"
msgstr "Contraataque en Mortain"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/name_big"
msgid "Mortain Counterattack"
msgstr "Contraataque en Mortain"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/narrator/01"
msgid ""
"Alright, stop it gentlemen! The 119th Infantry Regiment should be straight "
"in front of us. "
msgstr ""
"¡Muy bien, deténganse caballeros! El 119º Regimiento de Infantería debería "
"estar justo frente a nosotros. "

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/narrator/02"
msgid ""
"I couldn't reach anyone from the 119th, but I can see their position ahead "
"as marked on the map. Move the tanks slowly around the bend, it could be a "
"trap."
msgstr ""
"No pude contactar a nadie del 119, pero puedo según el mapa deberían estar "
"justo delante. Avanza lentamente con los tanques por la curva, podría ser "
"una trampa."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/narrator/03"
msgid ""
"God damn it! We're being fired upon! That is not the 119th. Germans, here?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldita sea! ¡Nos están disparando! Ese no es el 119. ¡¿Alemanes, aquí?!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/narrator/04"
msgid ""
"Infantry! Flank that roadblock and silence the AT gun. Our tanks cannot go "
"through the hedgerows, and the road is a choke point!"
msgstr ""
"¡Infantería! Flanqueen esa barricada y silencien el cañón AT. ¡Nuestros "
"tanques no pueden atravesar los setos, y la carretera es un cuello de "
"botella!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/narrator/05"
msgid "Good job! Now our column can move forward again."
msgstr "Buen trabajo Ahora nuestra formación puede volver a avanzar."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/narrator/06"
msgid "Panther! Panther blocking the road! Combat spread!"
msgstr "¡Panther! ¡Un Panther bloqueando el camino! ¡Formación de combate!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/narrator/07"
msgid ""
"Alright, I need that Panther to be taken out! Take the infantry carriers and "
"flank the enemy through the west. We cannot risk losing more tanks, and "
"we're no match for a Panther's frontal armour."
msgstr ""
"¡Muy bien, necesito a ese Panther fuera de combate! Coge los carros de "
"infantería y flanquea al enemigo por el oeste. No podemos arriesgarnos a "
"perder más tanques, y no somos rival para el blindaje frontal de un Panther."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/narrator/08"
msgid ""
"Good work taking the Panther now. You've definitely shown your tactical "
"prowess, and for this reason I place the remaining Shermans under your "
"command. Your orders are to take the village of Le-Mesnil-Adelée with our "
"remaining armour."
msgstr ""
"Buen trabajo con ese Panther. Definitivamente has demostrado tu destreza "
"táctica, y por esta razón voy a poner a los Shermans restantes bajo tu "
"mando. Tienes órdenes de tomar la aldea de Le-Mesnil-Adelée con nuestras "
"tropas restantes."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/narrator/09"
msgid ""
"Watch out for these Panzergrenadiers. They've got plenty of AT weapons and "
"move around quite fast with those pesky Hanomags."
msgstr ""
"Cuidado con los Panzergrenadiers. Tienen un montón de armamento antitanque y "
"se mueven muy rápido con esos malditos Hanomags."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/narrator/10"
msgid "They're retreating! "
msgstr "¡Se retiran! "

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/narrator/11"
msgid ""
"Never mind, they're not retreating, they're regrouping! This must be their "
"main assault! More panthers!"
msgstr ""
"Olvídalo, no se están retirando, ¡se están reagrupando! ¡Esta debe ser su "
"fuerza principal! ¡Más panthers!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/narrator/12"
msgid ""
"Reinforcements are at your disposal. Maintain control of that village, "
"Lieutenant. "
msgstr ""
"Los refuerzos están a su disposición. Mantenga el control de esa aldea, "
"Teniente. "

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/narrator2/01"
msgid "Aye, Sir. "
msgstr "Sí, señor. "

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/narrator2/02"
msgid "Alright, boys, we have places to go, keep moving! .... "
msgstr "Muy bien, chicos, tenemos sitios a los que ir, ¡avancen! .... "

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Well done! You just repelled a huge German counterattack. The threat of a "
"breakthrough is off the table now, and your tactical skill has not gone "
"unnoticed. Who knows, maybe General Watson will even reward you for this. "
"Keep it up!"
msgstr ""
"¡Bien hecho! Acaba de repeler un enorme contraataque alemán. La amenaza de "
"un nuevo avance ya no está sobre la mesa, y su habilidad táctica no ha "
"pasado desapercibida. Quién sabe, tal vez el General Watson le recompense "
"por esto. ¡Siga así!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"Ouch! That was not the outcome we planned for. The Germans will be able to "
"break through to Brittany now. How are we going to explain this to General "
"Watson?"
msgstr ""
"¡Ouch! Ese no era el resultado que habíamos planeado. Los alemanes serán "
"capaces de avanzar por Bretaña ahora. ¿Cómo vamos a explicar esto al General "
"Watson?"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/place"
msgid "3rd Armored Division “Spearhead”"
msgstr "3ª División Blindada \"Spearhead\""

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/recapture"
msgid "Recapture the roadblock!"
msgstr "¡Recupera el bloqueo del camino!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/story"
msgid " August 7th, 1944. You have been in France for two months now, and there’s no end in sight. Operation Cobra was a success, and the breakout from Normandy is a fact. Officially, Operation Cobra ended yesterday. Today, the enemy is counterattacking from the area of Mortain!\n\n We have orders to support the infantry that is taking the brunt of the counteroffensive. Move your armored column forward on the road to le Mesnil- Adelee, to establish contact with the 199th infantry Regiment at their roadblock, south of the town. When you get there, assess the situation and act accordingly. Your goal is to take the village. You must maintain a high level of situational awareness at all times, and keep communications to HQ open for further orders.\n\nGood luck!"
msgstr ""
"7 de agosto de 1944. Llevas dos meses en Francia,\n"
"\n"
"y no parece que te vayas a ir pronto.\n"
"\n"
"La Operación Cobra fue un éxito, y la salida de\n"
"\n"
"Normandía es un hecho.\n"
"\n"
"Oficialmente, la Operación Cobra terminó ayer.\n"
"\n"
"¡Hoy, el enemigo está contraatacando desde el área\n"
"\n"
"de Mortain! Tenemos órdenes de apoyar a la infantería..\n"
"\n"
"que se está llevando la peor parte del contraataque.\n"
"\n"
"Mueva sus tropas blindadas hacia adelante por el camino\n"
"\n"
"a le Mesnil- Adelee, para establecer contacto con el 199 Regimiento\n"
"\n"
"de infantería en el bloqueo del camino, al sur de la ciudad.\n"
"\n"
"Cuando llegues allí, evalúa la situación y\n"
"\n"
"actúa en consecuencia. Tu objetivo es tomar el pueblo.\n"
"\n"
"Debes mantener un alto nivel de conciencia\n"
"\n"
"situacional en todo momento, y mantener las comunicaciones\n"
"\n"
"con el Cuartel General para nuevas órdenes. ¡Mucha suerte!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_08_mortain/task4"
msgid "Fend off the main enemy force."
msgstr "Deshazte de la fuerza principal enemiga."
